| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-6031 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 9459af8e-f85b-51fc-9e6d-79a0213b396b"
